==Knockout stage==
{{Main|2013 CECAFA Cup knockout stage}}
The knockout stage began on 7 December with the [[#Quarter-finals|quarter-finals]] and ended on 12 December with the [[#Final|final]]. In this stage, teams [[Single-elimination tournament|played against each other once]], with the losers of the [[2013 CECAFA Cup knockout stage#Semi-finals|semi-finals]] playing against each other in a [[third place playoff]].

===Bracket===
{{2013 CECAFA Cup bracket}}

